    <string name="readme_title">Readme</string>
    <string name="readme_content">• IMPORTANT: Full protection requires both apps to be installed on the same device. If they are not on the same device, full protection cannot be achieved.\n\n• ON = restriction active.\n\n• To set Device Owner: the device must have no account. ADB: adb shell dpm set-device-owner app.secondway.lock/.DeviceAdminReceiver\n\n• How to uninstall: a Device Owner app cannot be uninstalled from Settings. Either factory reset the device, or remove Device Owner first via this app (button below) or ADB: adb shell dpm remove-active-admin app.secondway.lock/.DeviceAdminReceiver</string>
